{"tid":2499330,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"我決定左會係30號買人生第一部埃咩，你呢？","createTime":"2021-04-21T22:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:45:13.000Z","uid":37146,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7698104e740e154299cc2900abf4ad1c9397cb8b","tid":2499330,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:18:34.000Z","msg":"幾個月前部電腦死撚左SSD，而家勉強用住，但開始頂唔順，又嘈，又慢，都用左成9年，係時候叫佢死埋一邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新埃咩出左，雖然個樣柒左啲，又冇M1X，不過好多人都話好抵，買4.5K MON送電腦，我就未用過4K MON，又未用過其他咩既系列，新鍵盤仲有TOUCH ID，M1晶片又靜又勁，今次升級應該會好有感，期待！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"violet\"><span class=\"x-large\"><strong>買咩色好呀屌，黃色/橙色好似唔錯...</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dbabce479e0b627a276c6d4cf71db605350d2b","tid":2499330,"uid":198130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:20:49.000Z","msg":"是撚蛋啦買咪買囉"},{"pid":"078e16102a9d29dd73fb1e143547b5761c0ae2ed","tid":2499330,"uid":391632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:43:30.000Z","msg":"買咩色都好<br />\n唔好買平民色<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4df6cf525582370ba6629c09bb2d6846bf8ea90b","tid":2499330,"uid":81309,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:43:58.000Z","msg":"典解呢個post硬係有d鄉音<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8d41d86574e93f2a6eb8cc17379a95e431c7e6e","tid":2499330,"uid":37146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f9dbabce479e0b627a276c6d4cf71db605350d2b","tid":2499330,"uid":198130,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:20:49.000Z","msg":"是撚蛋啦買咪買囉"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T22:49:26.000Z","msg":"緊係買埃咩啦，就算而家砌部WIN機啲顯示卡俾人炒到貴撚晒，我先唔做傻仔"},{"pid":"7e7aed0c8d4d89730f0c44cf25bce9a5c4c8e2ad","tid":2499330,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"078e16102a9d29dd73fb1e143547b5761c0ae